---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Chairman Message" description="Read the message from our Chairman.">
  <Hero title="Message from Our Chairman" />
  
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <!-- Chairman Photo -->
        <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-lg h-96 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-gray-500">Chairman Photo Placeholder</span>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Message Content -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary font-heading mb-2">
            A Message of Commitment
          </h2>
          <p class="text-secondary font-semibold mb-6">From the Desk of Our Chairman</p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
            <p>
              Dear Valued Clients, Partners, and Stakeholders,
            </p>
            <p>
              It is my distinct pleasure to welcome you to Mallik Group PLC. As we reflect on our 
              journey, I am immensely proud of what we have accomplished together. From our humble 
              beginnings to becoming a diversified business group, our commitment to excellence has 
              never wavered.
            </p>
            <p>
              At Mallik Group, we believe that success is not just measured by financial metrics, 
              but by the positive impact we create in the lives of our clients and communities. 
              Whether it's helping families achieve their immigration dreams, creating beautiful 
              homes, empowering businesses, or shaping future leaders through education - every 
              endeavor is driven by our core values of integrity, innovation, and excellence.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our vision for the future is clear: to continue growing while maintaining the highest 
              standards of service and ethical conduct. We are committed to investing in our people, 
              adopting cutting-edge technologies, and expanding our reach to serve more communities.
            </p>
            <p>
              I extend my heartfelt gratitude to our dedicated team, loyal clients, and valued partners 
              who have been instrumental in our success. Together, we will continue to build tomorrow, today.
            </p>
            <p class="font-semibold">
              Warm regards,<br/>
              <span class="text-primary">Chairman</span><br/>
              Mallik Group PLC
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
